  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186400/extras/5feb60018f1033101fe96574bdc684ba.avif?t=1771247434\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186400/extras_big/5feb60018f1033101fe96574bdc684ba.avif?t=1771247434 width=1560 height=504 /></span>Pirate Fighting Simulator is a free multiplayer island arena PVP shooter where you fight other players using awesome pirate weapons. There are also cosmetics that you can unlock with more coming, these cosmetics can be either hats, weapon skins or in the form of a title that sits underneath your username. The game also includes emotes so you can absolutely boogie down silly style after destroying an enemy gamer. There are also a few game modes one being TDM (Team Death Match) , FFA (Free For All) and KoTC (King of The Cannon). </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186400/extras/5feb60018f1033101fe96574bdc684ba.avif?t=1771247434\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186400/extras_big/5feb60018f1033101fe96574bdc684ba.avif?t=1771247434 width=1560 height=504 /></span>Pirate Fighting Simulator is a free multiplayer island arena PVP shooter where you fight other players using awesome pirate weapons. There are also cosmetics that you can unlock with more coming, these cosmetics can be either hats, weapon skins or in the form of a title that sits underneath your username. The game also includes emotes so you can absolutely boogie down silly style after destroying an enemy gamer. There are also a few game modes one being TDM (Team Death Match) , FFA (Free For All) and KoTC (King of The Cannon). </p>",
